296  pos = ppt->getPos();
297  P[num][0] = pos.x();
298  P[num][1] = pos.y();
299  P[num][2] = pos.z();
300 // P[num] = ppt->getPos();
301 
302  id[num] = static_cast<int>(ppt->getValue<int>(ptId_ref, 0));
303 
304  if(ptInstId_ref.isValid())
305  inst_id[num] = static_cast<int>(ppt->getValue<int>(ptInstId_ref, 0));
306  else
307  inst_id[num] = id[num];
308 
309 // cout << "IN - id : " << id[num] << "\tinst_id " << inst_id[num] << "\tnum " << num << endl;
310  ++num;
311  }
312 
313  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Cd_pt) {
314  num = 0;
315  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
316  ptAttr = static_cast<UT_Vector3>(ppt->getValue<UT_Vector3>(ptCd_ref, 0));
317  Cd[num][0] = ptAttr.x();
318  Cd[num][1] = ptAttr.y();
319  Cd[num][2] = ptAttr.z();
320 // cout << "IN - Cd: " << Cd[num] << endl;
321  ++num;
322  }
323  }
324 
325  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Alpha_pt) {
326  num = 0;
327  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
328  Alpha[num] = static_cast<fpreal32>(ppt->getValue<fpreal32>(ptAlpha_ref, 0));
329  ++num;
330 
331  }
332  }
333 
334  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_N_pt) {
335  num = 0;
336  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
337  ptAttr = static_cast<UT_Vector3>(ppt->getValue<UT_Vector3>(ptN_ref, 0));
338  N[num][0] = ptAttr.x();
339  N[num][1] = ptAttr.y();
340  N[num][2] = ptAttr.z();
341  ++num;
342  }
343  }
344 
345  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_v_pt) {
346  num = 0;
347  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
348  ptAttr = static_cast<UT_Vector3>(ppt->getValue<UT_Vector3>(ptV_ref, 0));
349  v[num][0] = ptAttr.x();
350  v[num][1] = ptAttr.y();
351  v[num][2] = ptAttr.z();
352  ++num;
353  }
354  }
355 
356  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_pscale_pt) {
357  num = 0;
358  if(ptPscale_ref.isValid())
359  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
360  pscale[num] = static_cast<fpreal32>(ppt->getValue<fpreal32>(ptPscale_ref, 0));
361  ++num;
362  }
363  }
364 
365 // cout << "IN - P: " << P[num] << "\tN: " << N[num]<< "\tCd: " << Cd[num] << "\tpscale: " << pscale[num] << endl;
366 
367  }
368  else {
369  // If we're not processing the points of the prims, get the attr's reference for the attrs the user wants to use
370  if(method == CLUSTER_CVEX_POINT) {
371  num = 0;
372  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
373  pos = ppt->getPos();
374  // P[num] = ppt->getPos();
375  P[num][0] = pos.x();
376  P[num][1] = pos.y();
377  P[num][2] = pos.z();
378  // Set the id and instance id to match the points id
379  id[num] = static_cast<int>(ppt->getValue<int>(ptId_ref, 0));
380  inst_id[num] = num;
381  // cout << "IN - P: " << P[num] << " " << pos.x() << " " << pos.y() << " " << pos.z() << " " << num << endl;
382  ++num;
383  }
384  }
385  // Else we're processing the primitives attributes
386  else {
387  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Cd_prim) {
388  num = 0;
389  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
390  primAttr = static_cast<UT_Vector3>(ppt->getValue<UT_Vector3>(primCd_ref, 0));
391  Cd[num][0] = primAttr.x();
392  Cd[num][1] = primAttr.y();
393  Cd[num][2] = primAttr.z();
394  ++num;
395  }
396  }
397 
398  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Alpha_prim) {
399  num = 0;
400  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
401  Alpha[num] = static_cast<fpreal32>(ppt->getValue<fpreal32>(primAlpha_ref, 0));
402  ++num;
403  }
404  }
405 
406  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_N_prim) {
407  num = 0;
408  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
409  primAttr = static_cast<UT_Vector3>(ppt->getValue<UT_Vector3>(primN_ref, 0));
410  N[num][0] = primAttr.x();
411  N[num][1] = primAttr.y();
412  N[num][2] = primAttr.z();
413  ++num;
414  }
415  }
416 
417  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_v_prim) {
418  num = 0;
419  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
420  primAttr = static_cast<UT_Vector3>(ppt->getValue<UT_Vector3>(primV_ref, 0));
421  v[num][0] = primAttr.x();
422  v[num][1] = primAttr.y();
423  v[num][2] = primAttr.z();
424  ++num;
425  }
426  }
427 
428  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_pscale_prim) {
429  num = 0;
430  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
431  pscale[num] = static_cast<fpreal32>(ppt->getValue<fpreal32>(primPscale_ref, 0));
432  ++num;
433  }
434  }
435 
436  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_PRIM_METABALL && myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_weight_prim) {
437  num = 0;
438  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
439  weight[num] = static_cast<fpreal32>(ppt->getValue<fpreal32>(primWeight_ref, 0));
440  ++num;
441  }
442  }
443 
444  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
445  num = 0;
446  id[num] = static_cast<int>(ppt->getValue<int>(primId_ref, 0));
447  inst_id[num] = num;
448  ++num;
449  }
450 
451  }
452  }
453 
454 
455 #ifdef DEBUG
456  std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Finished storing attributes" << std::endl;
457 #endif
458 
459  // Add the inputs to the VEX call
460  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_POINT) {
461  cvex.addInput("P", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, P, num_points);
462  cvex.addInput("id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER, id, num_points);
463  cvex.addInput("inst_id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER, inst_id, num_points);
464 
465  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Cd_pt)
466  cvex.addInput("Cd", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, Cd, num_points);
467  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Alpha_pt)
468  cvex.addInput("Alpha", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT, Alpha, num_points);
469  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_N_pt)
470  cvex.addInput("N", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, N, num_points);
471  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_v_pt)
472  cvex.addInput("v", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, v, num_points);
473  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_pscale_pt)
474  cvex.addInput("pscale", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT, pscale, num_points);
475  }
476  else {
477  if(method == CLUSTER_CVEX_POINT) {
478  cvex.addInput("P", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, P, num_points);
479  cvex.addInput("id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER, id, num_points);
480  cvex.addInput("inst_id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER, inst_id, num_points);
481  }
482  else {
483  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Cd_prim)
484  cvex.addInput("Cd", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, Cd, num_prim);
485  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Alpha_prim)
486  cvex.addInput("Alpha", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT, Alpha, num_prim);
487  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_N_prim)
488  cvex.addInput("N", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, N, num_prim);
489  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_v_prim)
490  cvex.addInput("v", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3, v, num_prim);
491  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_pscale_prim)
492  cvex.addInput("pscale", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT, pscale, num_prim);
493 
494  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_PRIM_METABALL && myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_weight_prim)
495  cvex.addInput("weight", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT, weight, num_prim);
496 
497  cvex.addInput("id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER, id, num_prim);
498  cvex.addInput("inst_id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER, inst_id, num_prim);
499  }
500 
501  }
502 
503  // Add the motion blur pass flag
504  cvex.addInput("mb_pass", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER, &mb_pass, 1);
505  // Add a time input parm
506  cvex.addInput("time", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT, &time, 1);
507 
508 #ifdef DEBUG
509  std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Added inputs" << std::endl;
510 #endif
511 
512 
513  // Load the VEX function
514  char * cvexArgs[2];
515 // cvexArgs[0] = myCVEXFname;
516  cvexArgs[0] = theCVEXFname;
517  if(!cvex.load(1, cvexArgs)) {
518  std::cerr << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Unable to load cvex function:" << std::endl << cvexArgs[0] << std::endl;
519  throw VRAY_clusterThis_Exception("VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Unable to load cvex function, exiting VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() ...", 1);
520  }
521 
522 
523  if(myVerbose == CLUSTER_MSG_DEBUG)
524  std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Loaded VEX Function" << std::endl;
525 
526  CVEX_Value * P_val = NULL, *N_val = NULL, *v_val = NULL, *Cd_val = NULL, *Alpha_val = NULL,
527  *pscale_val = NULL, *id_val = NULL, *inst_id_val = NULL, *weight_val = NULL;
528 
529 
530  // Find the inputs of the loaded VEX function
531  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_POINT) {
532 
533  P_val = cvex.findInput("P", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
534 
535  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Cd_pt)
536  Cd_val = cvex.findInput("Cd", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
537  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Alpha_pt)
538  Alpha_val = cvex.findInput("Alpha", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
539  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_N_pt)
540  N_val = cvex.findInput("N", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
541  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_v_pt)
542  v_val = cvex.findInput("v", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
543  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_pscale_pt)
544  pscale_val = cvex.findInput("pscale", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
545  }
546  else {
547  if(method == CLUSTER_CVEX_POINT) {
548  P_val = cvex.findInput("P", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
549  }
550  else {
551  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Cd_prim)
552  Cd_val = cvex.findInput("Cd", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
553  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Alpha_prim)
554  Alpha_val = cvex.findInput("Alpha", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
555  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_N_prim)
556  N_val = cvex.findInput("N", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
557  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_v_prim)
558  v_val = cvex.findInput("v", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
559  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_pscale_prim)
560  pscale_val = cvex.findInput("pscale", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
561 
562  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_PRIM_METABALL && myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_weight_prim)
563  weight_val = cvex.findInput("weight", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
564  }
565 
566  }
567 
568  id_val = cvex.findInput("id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER);
569  inst_id_val = cvex.findInput("inst_id", CVEX_TYPE_INTEGER);
570 
571 
572  if(myVerbose == CLUSTER_MSG_DEBUG) {
573  dumpValueList("VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Input Parameters", cvex.getInputList());
574  }
575 
576  // dumpValue(P_val);
577  // dumpValue(N);
578  // dumpValue(v);
579  // dumpValue(Cd);
580  // dumpValue(Alpha);
581  // dumpValue(pscale);
582  // dumpValue(weight);
583 
584 
585 // std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Prepared arrays" << std::endl;
586 
587  CVEX_Value * P_out = NULL, *N_out = NULL, *Cd_out = NULL, *v_out = NULL, *Alpha_out = NULL, *pscale_out = NULL, *weight_out = NULL;
588 
589 
590  // Now find the outputs of the loaded VEX function
591  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_POINT) {
592 
593  P_out = cvex.findOutput("POut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
594 
595  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Cd_pt)
596  Cd_out = cvex.findOutput("CdOut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
597  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Alpha_pt)
598  Alpha_out = cvex.findOutput("AlphaOut", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
599  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_N_pt)
600  N_out = cvex.findOutput("NOut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
601  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_v_pt)
602  v_out = cvex.findOutput("vOut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
603  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_pscale_pt)
604  pscale_out = cvex.findOutput("pscaleOut", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
605  }
606  else {
607  if(method == CLUSTER_CVEX_POINT) {
608  P_out = cvex.findOutput("POut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
609  }
610  else {
611 
612  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Cd_prim)
613  Cd_out = cvex.findOutput("CdOut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
614  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Alpha_prim)
615  Alpha_out = cvex.findOutput("AlphaOut", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
616  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_N_prim)
617  N_out = cvex.findOutput("NOut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
618  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_v_prim)
619  v_out = cvex.findOutput("vOut", CVEX_TYPE_VECTOR3);
620  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_pscale_prim)
621  pscale_out = cvex.findOutput("pscaleOut", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
622 
623  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_PRIM_METABALL && myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_weight_prim)
624  weight_out = cvex.findOutput("weightOut", CVEX_TYPE_FLOAT);
625 
626  }
627  }
628 
629 
630  //if (!P_out && !N_out && !v_out && !Cd_out && !Alpha_out && !pscale_out && !weight_out)
631  // std::cerr << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - " << cvexArgs[0] << " doesn't seem to write to P, N, v, Cd, Alpha, pscale and weight ...???" << std::endl;
632 
633  // Setup the output arrays to prepare to recevve the processed VEX data
634  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_POINT) {
635  if(P_out)
636  P_out->setData(POut, num_points);
637  if(Cd_out)
638  Cd_out->setData(CdOut, num_points);
639  if(Alpha_out)
640  Alpha_out->setData(AlphaOut, num_points);
641  if(N_out)
642  N_out->setData(NOut, num_points);
643  if(v_out)
644  v_out->setData(vOut, num_points);
645  if(pscale_out)
646  pscale_out->setData(pscaleOut, num_points);
647  }
648  else {
649 
650  if(method == CLUSTER_CVEX_POINT) {
651 
652  if(P_out) {
653  P_out->setData(POut, num_points);
654  // std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Set POut successfully num_points: " << num_points << std::endl;
655  }
656  }
657  else {
658 
659  if(Cd_out)
660  Cd_out->setData(CdOut, num_prim);
661  if(Alpha_out)
662  Alpha_out->setData(AlphaOut, num_prim);
663  if(N_out)
664  N_out->setData(NOut, num_prim);
665  if(v_out)
666  v_out->setData(vOut, num_prim);
667  if(pscale_out)
668  pscale_out->setData(pscaleOut, num_prim);
669  if(weight_out && myPrimType == CLUSTER_PRIM_METABALL)
670  weight_out->setData(weightOut, num_prim);
671  }
672 
673  }
674 
675 
676 
677  if(myVerbose == CLUSTER_MSG_DEBUG)
678  std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Calling VEX code in .vex file: " << theCVEXFname << std::endl;
679 
680 
681  // Run the CVEX code
682  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_POINT) {
683  if(!cvex.run(num_points, false)) {
684  std::cerr << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - VEX function call failed!" << std::endl;
685  return 1;
686  }
687  }
688 
689  else {
690  if(method == CLUSTER_CVEX_POINT) {
691  if(!cvex.run(num_points, false)) {
692  std::cerr << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - VEX function call failed!" << std::endl;
693  return 1;
694  }
695  }
696  else {
697  if(!cvex.run(num_prim, false)) {
698  std::cerr << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - VEX function call failed!" << std::endl;
699  return 1;
700  }
701  }
702 
703  }
704 
705 
706  if(myVerbose == CLUSTER_MSG_DEBUG)
707  std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Finished running VEX code" << std::endl;
708 
709  if(myVerbose == CLUSTER_MSG_DEBUG) {
710  dumpValueList("VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Output Parameters", cvex.getOutputList());
711  }
712 
713  /*
714  dumpValue(P_out);
715  dumpValue(N_out);
716  dumpValue(v_out);
717  dumpValue(Cd_out);
718  dumpValue(Alpha_out);
719  dumpValue(pscale_out);
720  dumpValue(weightOut);
721  */
722 
723  num = 0;
724 
725  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_POINT) {
726 
727  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
728 
729  pos.x() = POut[num][0];
730  pos.y() = POut[num][1];
731  pos.z() = POut[num][2];
732 // pos = POut[num];
733  pos.w() = 1.0;
734  ppt->setPos(pos);
735 
736  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Cd_pt) {
737  ppt->setValue<UT_Vector3>(ptCd_ref, (const UT_Vector3)CdOut[num]);
738  }
739 
740  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_Alpha_pt) {
741  ppt->setValue<fpreal32>(ptAlpha_ref, (const fpreal32)AlphaOut[num]);
742  }
743 
744  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_N_pt) {
745  ppt->setValue<UT_Vector3>(ptN_ref, (const UT_Vector3)NOut[num]);
746  }
747 
748  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_v_pt) {
749  ppt->setValue<UT_Vector3>(ptV_ref, (const UT_Vector3)vOut[num]);
750  }
751 
752  if(myCVEXPointVars.cvex_pscale_pt) {
753  ppt->setValue<fpreal32>(ptPscale_ref, (const fpreal32)pscaleOut[num]);
754  }
755 
756 // cout << "OUT - POut: " << POut[num] << "\tNOut: " << NOut[num] << "\tCdOut: "
757 // << CdOut[num] << "\tpscaleOut: " << pscaleOut[num] << endl;
758 
759  ++num;
760  }
761  }
762 
763  else {
764 
765  if(method == CLUSTER_CVEX_POINT) {
766  num = 0;
767  GA_FOR_ALL_GPOINTS(cvex_gdp, ppt) {
768  pos.x() = POut[num][0];
769  pos.y() = POut[num][1];
770  pos.z() = POut[num][2];
771  // pos = POut[num];
772  pos.w() = 1.0;
773  ppt->setPos(pos);
774 // cout << "OUT - P: " << POut[num] << " " << pos.x() << " " << pos.y() << " " << pos.z() << " " << num << endl;
775  ++num;
776  }
777 
778  }
779  else {
780  num = 0;
781  GA_FOR_ALL_PRIMITIVES(cvex_gdp, prim) {
782 
783  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Cd_prim) {
784  prim->setValue<UT_Vector3>(primCd_ref, (const UT_Vector3)CdOut[num]);
785  }
786 
787  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_N_prim) {
788  prim->setValue<UT_Vector3>(primN_ref, (const UT_Vector3)NOut[num]);
789  }
790 
791  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_v_prim) {
792  prim->setValue<UT_Vector3>(primV_ref, (const UT_Vector3)vOut[num]);
793  }
794 
795  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_Alpha_prim) {
796  prim->setValue<float>(primAlpha_ref, (const float)AlphaOut[num]);
797  }
798 
799  if(myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_pscale_prim) {
800  prim->setValue<fpreal32>(primPscale_ref, (const fpreal32)pscaleOut[num]);
801  }
802 
803  if(myPrimType == CLUSTER_PRIM_METABALL && myCVEXPrimVars.cvex_weight_prim) {
804  prim->setValue<float>(primWeight_ref, (const float)weightOut[num]);
805  }
806 
807  ++num;
808  }
809  }
810 
811  }
812 
813  } // for (pass < num_passes) ...
814 
815  // std::cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Successfully set P, N, v, Cd, Alpha, pscale and weight" << std::endl;
816 
817  memCleaner.cleanUp(P, POut, N, NOut, v, vOut, Cd, CdOut, weight, weightOut, Alpha, AlphaOut, pscale, pscaleOut, id, inst_id);
818 
819  }
820 
821  catch(VRAY_clusterThis_Exception e) {
822  e.what();
823  memCleaner.cleanUp(P, POut, N, NOut, v, vOut, Cd, CdOut, weight, weightOut, Alpha, AlphaOut, pscale, pscaleOut, id, inst_id);
824 
825  return 1;
826  }
827 
828  catch(std::bad_alloc) {
829  cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Failed memory allocation, freeing geometry and exiting" << endl << endl;
830  memCleaner.cleanUp(P, POut, N, NOut, v, vOut, Cd, CdOut, weight, weightOut, Alpha, AlphaOut, pscale, pscaleOut, id, inst_id);
831 
832  return 1;
833  }
834 
835  catch(...) {
836  cout << "VRAY_clusterThis::runCVEX() - Unknown exception encountered, freeing geometry and exiting" << endl << endl;
837  memCleaner.cleanUp(P, POut, N, NOut, v, vOut, Cd, CdOut, weight, weightOut, Alpha, AlphaOut, pscale, pscaleOut, id, inst_id);
838 
839  return 1;
840  }
841 
842
